Read threshold value plugin
----------------------------

This is a third party web service to read the threshold value from the moodle database. This web service returns the threshold value stored for a particular courseid. This web service requires the courseid as an input parameter. 

To make the webservice working:
1- install the plugin in moodle/local/get_threshold
2- Read, setup and run moodle/local/get_threshold/client/client.php

Features:
---------
Protocol used: REST
Result format: XML or JSON
Function name: get_data
Input parameter: courseid	

Security is also taken into account by cross checking the token of the user with the token provided in the webservice call.
